title: fanoutqa: What are the 3 most common law schools attended by members of the US Supreme Court? (832e7529292aa805)

chat_history.content: What are the 3 most common law schools attended by members of the US Supreme Court?

Here are the top three most common law schools attended by members of the US Supreme Court:

1. Harvard University (16 justices)
2. Yale University (11 justices)
3. Columbia University (7 justices)
